comments: Smart (BOS) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Iguodala's (MIA) path.
Adebayo (MIA) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Brown's (BOS) path and does not deliver any contact.
Adebayo (MIA) legally contest Brown's (BOS) jump shot attempt.
Herro (MIA) does not make contact with Williams' (BOS) arm during the play at the basket.
Robinson (MIA) makes contact with Williams' (BOS) arm that affects his ability to pass.
Butler (MIA) makes leg to leg contact with Tatum (BOS) that affects his SQBR at the end of the drive.
Adebayo (MIA) legally contest Tatum's (BOS) jump shot attempt.
Williams (BOS) makes marginal contact with Adebayo (MIA) after the release of the pass and does not affect Adebayo's ability to pass.

Tatum (BOS) makes marginal contact with Robinson's (MIA) left arm after the release of the jump shot and does not affect Robinson's ability to completely follow through. The reaction is not consistent with the level of contact.
Brown (BOS) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Dragic's (MIA) path and does not deliver any contact.
Adebayo (MIA) legally blocks Smart's (BOS) driving shot attempt.
Butler (MIA) momentarily places an arm around Theis (BOS) as the screen concludes.
Theis (BOS) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Butler's (MIA) path and does not deliver any contact.
Butler (MIA) makes marginal contact with Theis' (BOS) arm during the play at the basket.
Butler (MIA) makes incidental foot to foot contact with Theis (BOS) during the rebound.
Adebayo (MIA) places a hand on Tatum's (BOS) back during the rebound, but does not deliver contact that impedes Tatum's ability to rebound.
There is no clear and conclusive video evidence that Smart (BOS) brings his non-dribbling hand in contact with the ball.
Robinson (MIA) makes contact to Smart's (BOS) shoulder that affects his driving shot attempt.
Williams III (BOS) momentarily grasps Adebayo's (MIA) jersey, then releases and makes clean hand on ball contact.
